| SimpleJWT | latest | JWT authentication |
| PostgreSQL | 15 | Primary database |
| Redis | latest | Caching + Pub/Sub |
| Apache Kafka | 7.4.0 | Message streaming |
| Zookeeper | 7.4.0 | Kafka coordinator |
| Docker + Compose | latest | Infrastructure |

---

## ✨ Features

- **JWT Authentication** — register, login, logout, token refresh
- **Room Management** — create, list, join, leave rooms
- **Auto-Delete** — room and all its messages are deleted when creator leaves
- **Real-time Messaging** — messages flow through Kafka → PostgreSQL + Redis
- **Redis Caching** — room membership and info cached for fast lookups
- **Pub/Sub** — Redis channels for real-time message broadcasting
- **Kafka Durability** — messages persisted in Kafka before DB write
- **Idempotent Consumer** — duplicate message protection via `get_or_create`
- **Cursor Pagination** — efficient message history with `before_id`
- **Monitoring UIs** — pgAdmin, Kafka UI, RedisInsight included

